caption.p: Three-dimensional ( right) and 2D (left) closest interactions between the active site residues of the human androgen and some molecules belonging to different class compounds with the best score result. Legend: ( A): Compound 15 (Selinidin, Class: coumarin derivative), ( B): Compound 18 (larixol acetate), ( C): Compound 19 (Valtratum, Class: Terpene) and ( D): Compound 22 (dihydrosamidin, Class: coumarins).
